name: Wealth and fund
description:
Wealth and fund is the title of this work.

The financial capitalist system has seized all the wealth and resources of the world. They have seized and restricted all human beings in the prison of money and wealth. The pig is a symbol of money and wealth, and the red mark indicates the result of these rules, and all its rules are for the basis of blood and money. Today, the world is facing financial constraints with the development of the Corona virus.

I will sell the file ready and Tif in the size of 10 x 10 cm and I will send it to the buyer.
